headline: USM's Q2 Earnings Beat Estimates Despite Lower Revenues
summary: USM's earnings beat estimates in the second quarter, with strong momentum in the tower business. Decline in prepaid and postpaid connections hindered growth.

headline: TDS Q2 Earnings Fall Short of Estimates, Revenues Decline Y/Y
summary: Telephone and Data Systems posts narrower loss as lower operating expenses, higher broadband connections and tower business growth help counter revenue declines in the second quarter.
